comment: Antetokounmpo (MIL) hand checks Pierce (WAS) on the perimeter and disrupts his RSBQ.
Ilyasova (MIL) is turning when contact occurs with Wall (WAS) on his drive.
Pierce (WAS) makes contact with Carter-Williams (MIL) from behind, but the contact does not dislodge Carter-Williams or affect his ability to pass.
Middleton (MIL) bumps Temple (WAS) as he drives on the baseline causing him to go OOB.
Gortat (WAS) sets a screen on Carter-Williams (MIL), giving him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Gortat (WAS) commits a take foul on Bayless (MIL).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) has two hands on Pierce (WAS), which is an automatic foul.
Temple (WAS) commits a take foul on Bayless (MIL).
